### Create Task
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "title": "Implement task API",
  "description": "Create handlers and routing",
  "priority": 2,
  "tags": ["backend", "fiber"]
}

### List Tasks (Pagination + Search) (JWT)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?page=1&limit=10&search=task&status=todo
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### List Tasks (Pagination + Search) (API Key)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?page=1&limit=10&search=task&status=todo
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Get Task By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/task-123
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Update Task
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/task-123
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "title": "Write final architecture doc",
  "priority": 4,
  "tags": ["architecture", "final"]
}

### Update Task Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/task-123/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "status": "done"
}

### Bulk Update Task Status
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "ids": [
    "task-123",
    "task-456",
    "task-789"
  ],
  "status": "in_progress"
}

### Delete Task
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/task-123
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Bulk Delete Tasks
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
